  Version bump with fixed SRC_URI. Remove old version with SRC_URI without
  arrow.

  16 Jun 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -bson-2.0.0.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

*bson-2.2.4 (01 Jun 2014)

  01 Jun 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +bson-2.2.4.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  26 May 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> bson-1.6.2-r1.ebuild,
